# --- harness data (results + gold are reproducible / large; not source) ---
# results/* = JSONL ledgers + results/transcripts/*.json · data/ = copied/symlinked gold · .worktrees/ = scratch worktrees per (infra_repo, ref)
# Published exceptions (sanitized by scripts/make_showcase.py — previews/paths/session
# ids stripped before the file exists): the public showcase ledger, and the DATED
# release-tracking snapshots (one per model generation; the raw working ledger
# results/claude5-refresh.jsonl stays ignored so resumed sweeps never append into a
# published file — each snapshot is immutable, guarded by tests/test_published_*.py).
results/*
!results/showcase.jsonl
!results/claude5-refresh-2026-07-06.jsonl
data/
.worktrees/
# .demo-infra/ = generated by examples/demo-infra/setup.sh (a local 2-ref git repo)
.demo-infra/
*.duckdb
.reviews/
